Playtest 2 — Stage 6 Round 5 Commit 6 baseline, NO SHOTS FIRED (controlled experiment).
Branch: main @ 9f5605e
Unity: 6000.4.6f1
Date: 2026-05-16
Purpose: isolate whether the Recover failure in playtest 1 was caused by pilot
incapacitation (damage hypothesis) or by an architectural stall-during-recovery
bug. By not firing, pilot HP stays at 80; if the AI still crashes, the
mechanism is architectural.

# CONCLUSION: AI crashed with the same Recover failure pattern as playtest 1
# despite no damage applied. Failure mode is architectural, not damage-related.

